    <label>Vat-grown megaspider</label>
    <description>Not actually a spider, the megaspider is a genetically-engineered giant insectoid the size of a bear. Designed for heavy work and combat, its thick chitinous armor makes it hard to kill, while its long deadly ripper-blades make it deadly. It is, however, quite slow in open terrain. A vat-grown creature, it is unable to reproduce, and its lifespan is significantly decreased.</description>
